  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <p class="faq-question">What is WanderlustFin?</p>
          <p class="faq-answer">WanderlustFin is a wealth identity platform that helps entrepreneurs and high-earners see their complete financial picture, understand their money patterns, and build wealth with clarity and intention.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <p class="faq-question">Is my financial data secure?</p>
          <p class="faq-answer">Absolutely. We use Plaid for all bank connections — the same technology trusted by Venmo, Robinhood, and major financial institutions. We never store your bank login credentials.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <p class="faq-question">What's a Wealth Archetype?</p>
          <p class="faq-answer">Your Wealth Archetype is your unique relationship pattern with money. Understanding it helps you make aligned decisions and build habits that match who you're becoming as a wealth steward.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <p class="faq-question">When is WanderlustFin launching?</p>
          <p class="faq-answer">We're currently in pre-launch. Join our waitlist to get early access and lock in founding member pricing before we open to the public.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <p class="faq-question">What accounts can I connect?</p>
          <p class="faq-answer">Via Plaid, you can connect checking accounts, savings accounts, high-yield savings (HYSA), investment/brokerage accounts, credit cards, and many insurance accounts.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <p class="faq-question">Do you offer refunds?</p>
          <p class="faq-answer">Yes! We offer a 14-Day Clarity Guarantee. If WanderlustFin doesn't bring you more financial clarity within 14 days, we'll refund your first month.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <p class="faq-question">Is this a budgeting app?</p>
          <p class="faq-answer">Not exactly. Traditional budgeting apps focus on restriction. WanderlustFin focuses on expansion, identity, and becoming the person who builds wealth — not just someone who tracks spending.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <p class="faq-question">Can I use this for my business finances?</p>
          <p class="faq-answer">Yes! Our Business Goal Tracker (available in Expansion tier and above) lets you track revenue goals, program launches, and business milestones alongside personal finances.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
